---
import { Button } from "@components/_button.tsx";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import { ExternalLinkIcon } from "lucide-react";
---

<div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-4 gap-3">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold font-serif underline">
        Cafe Niloufer - Hitech City
    </h2>
    <div id="logo">
        <Image
            src="https://cafeniloufer.com/cdn/shop/files/logo_360x_3a3f6a04-b109-4e88-97f9-b49ac4675c0d_360x.png?v=1619422169"
            loading="eager"
            priority
            inferSize
            alt="Cafe Niloufer Logo"
            format="webp, png"
            layout="full-width"
        />
    </div>
    <ul class="list-disc list-item">
        <li>
            The story of Cafe Niloufer began in 1978 with Shri. A. Babu Rao, who
            had a single vision of creating a Chai that was not just delicious
            in taste but also carried the spirit of the city of Hyderabad!
        </li>
        <li>
            Over the years, Cafe Niloufer has become an establishment that has
            upheld its own unique traditional taste of Hyderabadi Chai, becoming
            a household name in the process. From a single outlet in Lakdikapul,
            today Cafe Niloufer can also be enjoyed at Red Hills, Banjara Hills,
            Himayatnagar, RGI Airport and Hitec City
        </li>
        <li>
            With over 20,000 customers served every day, itâ€™s no secret that
            Hyderabad loves the Taste of Cafe Niloufer and it is our mission to
            make sure that this taste is one that we can always stay authentic
            to and preserve the tradition.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-3.5">
        <Button variant="link">
            <a
                href="https://cafeniloufer.com/"
                target="_blank"
                class="flex flex-row gap-2"
            >
                <ExternalLinkIcon size="lg" className="mt-1" /> Visit Website
            </a>
        </Button>
        <Button variant="link">
            <a
                href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/3Y3NX612TpY4zCy99"
                target="_blank"
                class="flex flex-row gap-2"
            >
                <ExternalLinkIcon size="lg" className="mt-1" /> Visit Location
            </a>
        </Button>
    </div>
</div>
